The purpose of the product is to ease color management. This is especially
usefull for designers.
Colorz is usable in many situations.
- It can automatically generate a color sheme for an entire website from only
  one single color!
- It serves as a single color repository for a website.
- You can change the color scheme for a branch of a website, or for the entire
  site without having to change any code.
- In systems like Plone, where changing the colors very often is part of site
  customisation procedure. Colorz makes it possible to change alle colors on a
  site by changing just the main color. Then the rest of the colors on the site
  will automatically adjust to this color by automatically generating an new
  color scheme. Following standard color theory.
